name anvil toast stack flow
navigate to http://127.0.0.1:5173
type alice@company.com into the email field
type platform into the team field
click Sign in
click Tasks
type First stacked task into the new-task field
click Add task
assert Added: First stacked task is visible
type Second stacked task into the new-task field
click Add task
assert Added: Second stacked task is visible
assert Added: First stacked task is visible
